%% Auto-Detection Sequence Diagram (REQ-006)
%% Shows the tiered detection from the user's perspective

sequenceDiagram
    participant U as Developer
    participant CC as Claude Code
    participant MPR as model-provider-router.cjs
    participant PU as provider-utils.cjs
    participant OLL as Ollama (localhost:11434)

    U->>CC: Runs "claude" in project
    CC->>CC: Loads CLAUDE.md
    U->>CC: Invokes a tool (e.g., Task)

    CC->>MPR: PreToolUse (stdin JSON)

    MPR->>MPR: Check tool_name === 'Task'
    MPR->>PU: hasProvidersConfig()
    PU-->>MPR: true (.isdlc/providers.yaml exists)

    MPR->>PU: loadProvidersConfig()
    PU-->>MPR: config {defaults.provider: "ollama", active_mode: "local"}

    MPR->>PU: selectProvider(config, state, context)

    Note over PU: Tier 1: Check env vars
    PU->>PU: ANTHROPIC_BASE_URL not set

    Note over PU: Tier 2: Check config file
    PU->>PU: defaults.provider = "ollama"

    Note over PU: Mode = "local" -> provider = "ollama"
    PU-->>MPR: {provider: "ollama", model: "qwen-coder", source: "mode_local"}

    MPR->>PU: selectWithFallback(config, selection)

    Note over PU: Tier 3: Health probe (only for Ollama)
    PU->>OLL: GET /api/tags
    OLL-->>PU: 200 OK (models list)
    PU-->>MPR: {healthy: true, latency_ms: 45}

    MPR->>PU: getEnvironmentOverrides(config, selection)
    PU-->>MPR: {ANTHROPIC_BASE_URL: "http://localhost:11434", ANTHROPIC_API_KEY: "", ANTHROPIC_AUTH_TOKEN: "ollama"}

    MPR->>CC: stdout JSON (env overrides)
    CC->>OLL: LLM request (via Anthropic Messages API)
    OLL-->>CC: LLM response
    CC-->>U: Tool result
